"GAMBIT (the Global And Modular BSM Inference Tool) is a software code for performing statistical global fits of generic physics models using a wide range of particle physics and astrophysics data."
"Assuming that you have retrieved the git repository or the tarball and unpacked it:" followed by build instructions using `cmake` and `make`.
